query:
SELECT ac.id FROM allergy_combinations AS ac
        WHERE (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM allergy_combinations INNER JOIN allergies ON allergies.id = allergy_combinations.allergy_id WHERE allergy_combinations.id = ac.id) =
            (SELECT COUNT(1) FROM allergy_combinations INNER JOIN allergies ON allergies.id = allergy_combinations.allergy_id INNER JOIN UNNEST($1::text[]) AS names(name) ON names.name = allergies.name WHERE allergy_combinations.id = ac.id)
